{"tid":1638270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阻華盜科研機密 FBI鎖定50大學","createTime":"2019-10-08T09:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:05:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e177a4e0cc17e26defeda3a6277b668e536a9cf8","tid":1638270,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:03:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191007/T6Y22PVZ736ZVPX7IYEMIOT2WY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191007%2FT6Y22PVZ736ZVPX7IYEMIOT2WY%2F&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=34132ff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191007%2FT6Y22PVZ736ZVPX7IYEMIOT2WY%2F&h=505b7b03\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191007/T6Y22PVZ736ZVPX7IYEMIOT2WY/</a><br />\n<br />\n阻華盜科研機密 FBI鎖定50大學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/byCi_MJ_Yua8RlE7Jp05ybL-WcU=/190x134/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/5A5BVMXJKWR6ASQFSB7DBBQ3HE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FbyCi_MJ_Yua8RlE7Jp05ybL-WcU%3D%2F190x134%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F5A5BVMXJKWR6ASQFSB7DBBQ3HE.jpg&h=3f815dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中美高層貿易談判本周末重啟。圖為美國洛杉磯一個碼頭堆放來自中國的貨櫃。<br />\n<br />\n過往美國法庭案例，見到中國往往從大學剽竊科技資訊及商業機密。美國政府近日似乎針對中國做法，將大學成為防止剽竊的「前線」，提醒大學有很多尖端研究，加上「有許多外國留學生」，「極可能成為外國勢力做為竊取資訊的目標」。<br />\n<br />\n發電郵助了解風險<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報道，香檳伊利諾大學（UIUC）助理副校監日前接獲聯邦調查局（FBI）電子郵件，查詢校方是否認為竊取了學校的任何智慧財產權。校方指未發現相關事件，FBI回應指預料學校有如此回應，「但我還是需要問一下」。報道透露他們取得50間公立大學的電郵，追查中國是否透過學術研究人員大量竊取科技資訊與商業機密，足證美國當局的決心。<br />\n<br />\n在FBI給予大學的郵件中，表明擔心美國大學內有尖端研究，加上校園有許多外國留學生，極可能成為外國勢力做為竊取資訊的目標，矛頭直指中國。電郵紀錄顯示，美國曾要求一位圓石市科羅拉多大學（University of Colorado Boulder）教授說明某些研究經費是否可能遭到誤用。司法部負責國家安全事務的助理部長戴莫斯（John Demers）說：「我們想做的是，希望讓校方了解某些風險的存在，但不希望讓學校因此不敢接受如中國的研究人員與學生。」<br />\n<br />\n世界日報"},{"pid":"c3935933141cd97fca3558bf8a10e8861363c904","tid":1638270,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554cb3e48cb1512170fca95950f2a0b4aaea223a","tid":1638270,"uid":331697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"遣返啲大陸人返去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33300785f203cd03afc5f856ffcb9c6914a00456","tid":1638270,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}